##############################################
#  LESSON 1.3  –  SUBJECTS & TOPICS HARDENING
##############################################

### 1. Get paginated subjects  (page 1, 5 per page)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/subjects?page=1&limit=5
Content-Type: application/json


### 2. Search subjects by keyword  (q = math)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/subjects?q=math
Content-Type: application/json


### 3. Filter subjects by grade level  (Grade 6)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/subjects?grade_level=Grade%206
Content-Type: application/json


### 4. Get topics for a subject  (id = 1)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/topics?subject_id=1
Content-Type: application/json


### 5. Filter topics by difficulty  (subject_id + difficulty)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/topics?subject_id=1&difficulty=med
Content-Type: application/json


### 6. Paginate topics  (page 1, 10 per page)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/topics?page=1&limit=10
Content-Type: application/json


### 7. Combine filters + pagination  (Grade 6 subjects containing “math”)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/subjects?q=math&grade_level=Grade%206&page=1&limit=5
Content-Type: application/json
